<item>
            <title>[LU-19481] FLR-EC: Basic do-no-harm lov IO support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19481</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Support for EC components not interfering with regular IO - both new and old clients (2.10 and later with FLR support) should be able to do &apos;normal&apos; IO on EC files with expected results.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No support for intent and layout state updates yet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
